          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-05-19 10:19:23" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>a woman of Greek culture and language</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>Greek woman</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is possible that in {S:04100702600010} Ἑλληνίς is to be understood in the sense of Gentile (see {D:11.41}), for the account seems to focus upon the fact that this woman who was not a Jewess nevertheless displayed remarkable faith and confidence in Jesus’ ability to help.</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
          </LEXSenses>
